---
import CssNakedDay from '../components/CssNakedDay/CssNakedDay.astro';
import HtmlHead from '../components/HtmlHead/HtmlHead.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo/Logo.astro';
import OldStyleButtons from '../components/OldStyleButtons/OldStyleButtons.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav/SiteNav.astro';
import SvgDefs from '../components/SvgDefs/SvgDefs.astro';
import Webrings from '../components/Webrings/Webrings.astro';
import { encodeEmail } from '../utils/email';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPage">
	<HtmlHead
		title="AI Use Statement | Marco Campos"
		description="AI Use Statement for Marco Campos website."
	/>
	<body>
		<a href="/yapping" rel="nofollow" hidden>Don't follow this link</a>

		<skip-to-content>
			<a href="#main">Skip to main content</a>
		</skip-to-content>

		<SiteNav />
		<CssNakedDay />

		<header>
			<Logo
				subtitle="AI Use"
				shortSubtitle="AI"
				title="Ai Use Page"
			/>
			<h1>AI Use Statement</h1>
		</header>

		<main id="main">
			<p>I do use AI tools to generate some of the content published on this website. Below are places and situations where AI is used, and those where it is not.</p>

			<h2>AI <em>is</em> used for</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>Hero images for posts</li>
				<li>Internal images on some posts</li>
				<li>Audio/song version of the website license</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>AI <em>is not</em> used for</h2>

			<ul>
				<li>Generating or writing code for the website</li>
				<li>Writing content for the website</li>
				<li>Designs for the website</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Is your art misused or stolen?</h2>

			<p>If you feel like your art have been stolen or scraped by AI, first I'm sorry.</p>
			<p>Although I cannot remove your art from the datasets used to train these AI models, what I <em>can</em> do is remove the results from my website.</p>
			<p>If you would like me to do so, please contact me at <em><Fragment set:html={`<a href="mailto:${encodeEmail(true)}">${encodeEmail()}</a>`} /></em>.</p>
			<p>If you have the technical knowledge, an alternative is to open an issue <a href="https://github.com/madcampos/madcampos/issues/new">on GitHub</a>.</p>
		</main>

		<footer>
			<OldStyleButtons />
			<Webrings />
			<hit-counter></hit-counter>
		</footer>
		<SvgDefs />
		<iab-escape></iab-escape>
	</body>
</html>
